item.title: HelloWorld
item.description: First Greetings who am I? I’m Myungjae, sophomore in UW-madison. I’ll be writing post frequently as possible, so keep it up! What do I do? I study computer science and data science. I’m into Machine Learning, Reinforcement learning, and making electronics using micro controllers!
